title: Tony Hawk
itunes:title: Tony Hawk
description:
Skating legend Tony Hawk and Whitney all things Tony Hawk. Don’t panic, Whitney's best friend Kevin Christy, comedian and skate history aficionado, joins in to geek out with Tony about NBDs, heelflips, nosegrabs, and vintage skate stickers. Check out Tony's podcast Hawk vs. Wolf, out now. 

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
